---
import ProductPage from "../layouts/ProductPage.astro";
const facts = [["Surface-aware kernel", "linux-surface, headers, libwacom-surface, and iptsd tailor the system for Surface touch, pen, keyboard, and platform hardware."], ["Graphics and firmware", "A current Mesa stack and broad backports firmware coverage support the graphics, wireless, audio, and peripheral hardware a mobile machine relies on."], ["The full Snow desktop", "Snowfield retains the same GNOME, software-layering, and workstation experience as Snow. The difference is the hardware focus, not a reduced desktop."]];
---
<ProductPage title="Snowfield" description="A Frostyard GNOME desktop tuned for Surface devices." active="images">
  <header class="hero"><p class="eyebrow"><i></i> Snowfield · Surface desktop</p><h1>Snow, shaped for<br /><em>the hardware in hand.</em></h1><p>Snowfield brings the Snow workstation to Surface devices with the linux-surface kernel and the supporting hardware stack already composed into the image.</p></header>
  <section class="signal"><span>SNOWFIELD</span><p>GNOME desktop · linux-surface · Touch and pen support</p></section>
  <section class="facts">{facts.map(([title, body], index) => <article><b>0{index + 1}</b><h2>{title}</h2><p>{body}</p></article>)}</section>
  <section class="bottom"><div><p class="eyebrow"><i></i> A focused variation</p><h2>One shared desktop.<br />A closer fit for Surface.</h2></div><p>Snowfield takes Snow’s desktop composition and changes the part that matters for Surface hardware: the kernel and its companion drivers, firmware, and input support.</p></section>
</ProductPage>
<style>
  .hero{padding:7rem 0 5rem;max-width:900px}.eyebrow{font-size:.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.17em;font-weight:700;color:#82b6d0;margin:0 0 1.1rem}.eyebrow i{display:inline-block;width:24px;height:1px;background:#47b8ef;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:.6rem}.hero h1,.bottom h2{font-size:clamp(3.4rem,6vw,6.4rem);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.075em;margin:0}.hero h1 em{font-family:Georgia,serif;font-weight:400;color:#aee9ff}.hero>p:last-child{font-size:1.08rem;color:#b6d0df;max-width:620px;margin:2rem 0 0}.signal{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#16455d,#0a2033);border:1px solid var(--line);padding:2rem 2.3rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}.signal span{font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.08em;color:#aee9ff}.signal p{font:.72rem ui-monospace,monospace;color:#91cee7;margin:0}.facts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);margin-top:1rem;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}.facts article{padding:2.5rem 2rem 2.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}.facts article+article{padding-left:2rem;border-left:1px solid var(--line)}.facts b{font:400 .7rem ui-monospace,monospace;color:#47b8ef}.facts h2{font-size:1.2rem;margin:.8rem 0}.facts p,.bottom>p{font-size:.9rem;color:#b6d0df;margin:0}.bottom{margin:7rem 0 5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr .8fr;gap:4rem;align-items:end}.bottom h2{font-size:clamp(2.3rem,3.8vw,4rem);margin:0}@media(max-width:720px){.hero{padding:5rem 0 4rem}.signal{display:block}.signal p{margin-top:.7rem}.facts,.bottom{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2rem}.facts article,.facts article+article{padding:1.8rem 0;border-left:0}.bottom{margin-top:5rem}}
</style>
